Developer Terms of Use
des: Third Space emulates the place where people work and gather collectively without having to actually be in one. It will bring to you ambient environments with sounds from different places where people work and gather collectively according to your individual tastes. The action provides the benefits of increased focus and the unique energy that can be found in spaces such as a library, coffee shop, or an office.
